These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-1::.
There 4 different types of food: onion, raspberry, tomato, watermelon
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, salsa, gospel, jazz
4 different pets are kept: fish, dog, guinea-pig, goldfish
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, car, helicopter, train
 1. the person driving the car is the fan of salsa##1
 2. the person eating tomato is the fan of gospel##1
 3. the owner of the fish is on the right of the person driving the train##1
 4. the owner of the dog is on the right of the fan of folk##1
 5. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
 6. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person driving the train##1
 7. the person driving the scooter is on the left or right of the fan of salsa##3
 8. the fan of jazz is somewhere to the left of the fan of gospel##5
 9. the fan of jazz is on the left or right of the fan of folk##3
10. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere to the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##5
11. the person driving the train is somewhere to the right of the person eating watermelon##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3   |    4     |
| Food          | watermelon     | raspberry   | onion | tomato |
| Music-Genre   | salsa | folk    | jazz   | gospel    |
| Pet           | guinea-pig       | goldfish   | dog   | fish     |
| Transport     | car       | scooter | train  | helicopter      |

