.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, water, 7up, lemonade
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, western, adventure, horror
4 different pets are kept: snake, mouse, rat, horse
The people use 4 different means of transport: taxi, bus, subway, snowmobile
 1. the person watching adventure movies is on the far right##1
 2. the owner of the rat is in an odd position##4
 3. the owner of the horse is the person drinking milk##1
 4. the person watching horror movies is somewhere to the right of the person driving the snowmobile##5
 5. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
 6. the person driving the snowmobile is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person watching disaster movies is between the person watching horror movies and the person drinking water##2
 8. the owner of the horse is somewhere to the left of the person driving the bus##5
 9. the owner of the mouse is the person watching horror movies##1
10. the owner of the horse is somewhere to the right of the person drinking water##5
11. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |      4       |
| Beverage      | water       | milk | lemonade     | 7up     |
| Movie-Genre   | western      | disaster       | horror | adventure |
| Pet           | rat       | horse    | mouse     | snake         |
| Transport     | snowmobile | subway     | taxi     | bus       |

