The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: superhero, musical, comedy, sports
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, disco, r&b, funk
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, ferret, horse, hamster
 1. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
 2. the owner of the hamster is on the left or right of the person watching sports movies##3
 3. the fan of house is somewhere to the right of the fan of disco##5
 4. the fan of funk is somewhere to the right of the owner of the hamster##5
 5. the person eating lettuce is on the left of the person eating cranberry##1
 6. the owner of the hamster is between the fan of funk and the fan of r&b##2
 7. the fan of house is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
 8. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere to the left of the owner of the ferret##5
 9. the owner of the rabbit is in an even position##4
10. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the person eating cranberry##1
11. the person watching comedy movies is the owner of the rabbit##1
12. the person watching superhero movies is somewhere to the left of the person eating potato##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | papaya    | potato      | lettuce   | cranberry |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | comedy | musical | sports  |
| Music-Genre   | disco   | r&b         | house  | funk  |
| Pet           | horse      | rabbit          | hamster | ferret  |

