The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, parkour, surfing, climbing
 1. the fan of rock is somewhere to the left of the dancer##5
 2. the fan of rock is on the left of the dressmaker##1
 3. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left or right of the bartender##3
 4. the person who's sport is parkour is somewhere to the right of the person drinking coffee##5
 5. the person who's sport is swimming is somewhere to the left of the person drinking lemonade##5
 6. the fan of hip-hop is on the left or right of the fan of rock##3
 7. the person drinking coffee is between the fan of hip-hop and the person drinking water##2
 8. the mechanic is on the far left##1
 9. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the fan of techno##3
10. the person drinking water is somewhere to the right of the person drinking lemonade##5
11. the fan of techno is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
12. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the right of the person drinking juice##5
13. the fan of hip-hop is somewhere to the left of the dancer##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |       3        |      4      |
| Beverage      | juice | lemonade     | coffee        | water      |
| Job           | mechanic    | dressmaker   | bartender | dancer |
| Music-Genre   | rock      | hip-hop    | trance        | techno         |
| Sport         | swimming    | surfing | climbing         | parkour    |

