 3. the french is in an odd position##4
 4. the lawyer is somewhere to the left of the person drinking milk##5
 5. the person eating pepper is the person drinking 7up##1
 6. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person eating pepper##1
 7. the person eating lettuce is on the left or right of the lawyer##3
 8. the australian is on the left or right of the paramedic##3
 9. the coach is somewhere to the right of the person eating lettuce##5
10. the person eating raspberry is on the far left or far right##3
11. the person eating raspberry is on the left or right of the argentine##3
12. the person drinking 7up is somewhere to the right of the person drinking mirinda##5
13. the australian is somewhere to the left of the person drinking milk##5

.:: Answer ::.
