.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |     3      |        4        |
| Beverage      | lemonade   | cola | almond-milk   | juice          |
| Food          | peach    | orange        | peas     | raspberry          |
| Job           | police-officer | coach        | photographer | firefighter |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy    | thriller     | satire      | horror        |

