.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, cola, mirinda, almond-milk
The people have 4 different jobs:  fisherman, videographer, project-manager, dressmaker
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: romance, adventure, time-travel, scientific
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, van, trike, helicopter
 1. the person driving the van is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person drinking cola is somewhere to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##5
 3. the dressmaker is on the left or right of the fisherman##3
 4. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
 5. the videographer is between the project-manager and the person watching scientific movies##2
 6. the person watching time-travel movies is in an odd position##4
 7. the project-manager is the person watching adventure movies##1
 8. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
 9. the person driving the trike is on the left or right of the person driving the van##3
10. the person driving the car is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
11. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
12. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the fisherman##1
13. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the right of the person watching time-travel movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Beverage      | mirinda   | almond-milk      | cola | tea     |
| Job           | dressmaker   | fisherman  | videographer        | project-manager |
| Movie-Genre   | romance     | scientific     | time-travel      | adventure   |
| Transport     | van | trike | helicopter          | car     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-20::.
There 4 different types of food: lettuce, orange, apple, grapes
The people have 4 different jobs:  doctor, coach, photographer, manager
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, epic, sports, thriller
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: techno, ambient, indie, disco
 1. the person eating apple is somewhere to the right of the person watching epic movies##5
 2. the fan of disco is the person eating lettuce##1
 3. the person eating apple is somewhere to the left of the fan of techno##5
 4. the doctor is in an even position##4
 5. the coach is on the left of the fan of indie##1
 6. the fan of techno is somewhere to the right of the fan of ambient##5
 7. the photographer is the person watching thriller movies##1
 8. the person watching thriller movies is somewhere to the left of the doctor##5
 9. the fan of indie is on the right of the person eating lettuce##1
10. the person watching thriller movies is somewhere to the right of the person eating apple##5
11. the person watching fantasy movies is somewhere to the right of the person eating grapes##5
12. the person watching epic movies is somewhere to the left of the person eating apple##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3       |     4      |
| Food          | lettuce | apple  | grapes    | orange       |
| Job           | coach  | manager | photographer | doctor  |
| Movie-Genre   | epic    | sports   | thriller  | fantasy     |
| Music-Genre   | disco      | indie    | ambient        | techno |

 